query:
INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved)
VALUES 
('Mark Randall', NULL, 5, 'I''ve been consistently impressed with the exceptional quality of service provided by All Resume Services. Every time I''ve applied for a job using the resume they crafted for me, I''ve landed an interview. Their professionalism and swift turnaround times are unparalleled. Not only does my resume look fabulous, but it also stands out in the competitive job market here in Australia. It''s worth every penny spent and I''m convinced that All Resume Services is the best in the business, and I couldn''t be more satisfied with the results. Highly recommend', NULL, 1, 1),
('Ali Al Obeid', NULL, 5, 'I paid for the resume and cover letter service and honestly was totally surprised by the results. I want to thank Sonia for an amazing cover letter and a very professional resume. I thought I already had a good resume but after seeing her work I was really impressed.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Naveen Karunaratne', NULL, 5, 'I reached out to Sonia and the team at All Resume Services a couple of years ago to have my resume and cover letter done upon moving to Australia. The service was extremely professional and prompt. I have had a lot of positive responses.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Peter Koikas', NULL, 5, 'I was referred to Allresume Services. Great experience. Assisted me with my resume, cover letter and LinkedIn profile. Did an awesome job. Very happy with everything presented. Highly recommend Sonia and her team.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Nrupa Shah', NULL, 5, 'Dear Sonia I hope this email finds you well. I wanted to take a moment to express my heartfelt gratitude for the fantastic resume and guidance you provided during my job search. I am excited to share that I have just accepted a position at SCE Group, and I couldn''t have done it without your help! Your expertise in showcasing my skills and experience truly made a difference. The feedback I received from interviewers was overwhelmingly positive, and I am confident your resume played a significant role in helping me stand out. Thank you once again for your professionalism, attention to detail, and for being such a wonderful support throughout this process.', NULL, 1, 1)
